dooyit.parser

Class ShowParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • dooyit.parser.ShowParser

  • public class ShowParser
extends java.lang.Object
    The ShowParser class takes in a "show" command input and returns a Command object. It is needed to switch between the standard views on the Dooyit application.
    Author:
    Annabel

        public Command getCommand(java.lang.String input)
        Parses userInput and returns a ShowCommand object
        Parameters:
        input - The show command input from the user
        Returns:
